a.xlink:title: ADS1x15 represents an ADS1015 or ADS1115 Analog to Digital Converter.
BMP280 represents an ADAfruit or compatible BMP280 temperature & pressure sensor.
DigitalInput is the base class for reading a digital GPIO pin.
DigitalInputChange is meant to report when a digital pin changes its state.
DigitalInputCounter counts interrupts and reports the count every read_delay ms.
